spring security oauth2.0 实现
没有与JWT结合


http://blog.csdn.net/monkeyking1987/article/details/16828059
Spring Security 与 Oauth2 整合 步骤 

与spring-security-oauth相比
token持久化到数据库里

----------------------------------------------------------
http://localhost:8080/spring-security-oauth
aa/aa

获取access_token  URL ：
http://localhost:8080/spring-security-oauth-02/oauth/token?client_id=mobile_1&client_secret=secret_1&grant_type=password&username=aa&password=aa


这之后再拿着这个access_token去访问资源：
http://localhost:8080/spring-security-oauth-02/admin?access_token=ee730849767a41bda52f3498a45d9162






